column2: SELECT m.ra, m.dec, m.specObjID, S.ra, S.dec, S.specObjID, S.mjd, S.plate, S.fiberID, S.class, S.z, S.zErr, S.rChi2, S.velDisp, S.velDispErr, dbo.fgeturlfitsspectrum (S.specobjid) , G.extinction_r, G.modelMag_u, G.modelMagErr_u, G.modelMag_g, G.modelMagErr_g, G.modelMag_r, G.modelMagErr_r, G.modelMag_i, G.modelMagErr_i, G.modelMag_z, G.modelMagErr_z, GSL.oii_#_flux, GSL.oii_#_flux_err, GSL.neiii_#_flux, GSL.neiii_#_flux_err, GSL.h_gamma_flux, GSL.h_gamma_flux_err, GSL.nii_#_flux, GSL.nii_#_flux_err, GSL.h_alpha_flux, GSL.h_alpha_flux_err, GSL.oiii_#_flux, GSL.oiii_#_flux_err, GSL.h_beta_flux, GSL.h_beta_flux_err, GSL.h_delta_flux, GSL.h_delta_flux_err, GSL.sii_#_flux, GSL.sii_#_flux_err, GSL.sii_#_flux, GSL.sii_#_flux_err, GSX.d4#, GSX.d4#_err INTO MyDB.chandra_unmatched_sdss_details1# FROM MyDB.chandra_unmatched_sdss AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEQ (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n, specObj AS S LEFT JOIN SpecPhoto AS G ON S.specObjID = G.specObjID LEFt JOIN GalSpecLine AS GSL ON S.specObjID = GSL.specObjID LEFT JOIN GalSpecIndx AS GSX ON S.specObjID = GSX.specObjID WHERE n.ObjID = S.bestObjID
